ary, making him one of the greatest swimmers the country has produced.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His four medals\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"one gold\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"three silver\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"any South African Olympian\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"a list\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"short-course achievements\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"a library\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest swimmers\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 963}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now 32, he is taking to the water in the100m butterflyand admits that he has a lot to do.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1080, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"the100m\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1035}, {\"ngram\": \"butterflyand\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am the third oldest male swimmer at these Games, so in those terms I am something of a pensioner.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the third oldest male swimmer\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"those terms\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"a pensioner\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And in spite of picking up a shoulder tear in training, I have come to Paris believing I have a chance.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1254, \"end\": 1259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998472380983, \"rank\": 1.5276204789103013e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"spite\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"a shoulder tear\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1237}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have raced with injuries before.\\\"\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Le Clos is a leader and a racer and although the odds seem to be against him adding to his medals tally in Paris, one also needs to acknowledge that if he gets to the final it's game on.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1431, \"end\": 1436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998472380983, \"rank\": 1.5276204789103013e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Le Clos\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"a leader\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"a racer\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1355}, {\"ngram\": \"the odds\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"his medals tally\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"game\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1506}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think that the semi-final will be the harder race, because there will be 16 swimmers going for a place in the final.\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the harder race\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1564}, {\"ngram\": \"16 swimmers\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am hoping to get there and once I do I will be chasing another dream.\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\":